ye-west-and-ty-dolla-igns-vultures-2-has-now-dropped-heres-how-people-are-reacting-3780628">《Vultures 2》引起了歌迷和评论家的褒贬不一的反应</a>，并且还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geoff-barrow-claims-kanye-west-ty-dolla-ign-didnt-have-permission-to-sample-portishead-on-vultures-2-3780721">引起了杰夫·巴罗 (Geoff Barrow) 的批评</a>，他暗示两位说唱歌手未经许可在《Vultures 2》曲目中采样了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/portishead">波蒂斯黑德 (Portishead)</a> 。</p><p> The <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beak">Beak>;</a>成员在 X/Twitter 上发布了一段由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/don-toliver">Don Toliver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kodak-black">Kodak Black</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>主演的“Field Trip”片段，据报道还试玩了 Portishead 的“Machine Gun”。</p><p> “FFS。不会再有一次”，他写道，似乎指的是另一次未经许可就拍摄歌曲的情况。 “他为什么不能写自己的节奏？”</p><p>最初的“Vultures”专辑也遇到了类似的涉嫌侵犯版权的问题， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-donna-summers-estate-reach-settlement-over-use-of-i-feel-love-3768363">West 和 Donna Summer 的遗产管理机构就“Vultures 1”中涉嫌“非法”使用“I Feel Love”达成和解</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-on-confronting-kanye-west-for-sampling-his-song-without-permission-its-wrong-if-you-dont-say-anything-about-him-3593757">奥兹·奥斯本还威胁要对未经授权的黑色安息日样品采取法律行动</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-a-brief-appearance-at-donald-trump-supporters-rally-in-beverly-hills-3784869">韦斯特和他的妻子比安卡·森索里最近出现</a>在比佛利山庄的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>集会上。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kanye-west-ride-a-horse-into-his-vultures-2-listening-experience-in-south-korea-3786287">观看坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 骑马进入韩国聆听《Vultures 2》体验的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
