门票销售低迷后，Sexyy Red 悄悄取消巡演日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-quietly-cancels-tour-dates-after-low-ticket-sales-3786239?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sexyy-red-quietly-cancels-低价售票后的巡演日期Laura MolloyFri, 23 Aug 2024 13:12:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopLive Music NewsRaphttps://www.nme.com/?p=3786239 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="性感红。图片来源：凯特琳·莫里斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于今年销量低迷，The Black Keys、Lauryn Hill and The Fugees 等乐队也取消了演出日期</p><p>《Sexyy Red》在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-quietly-cancels-tour-dates-after-low-ticket-sales-3786239">门票销售低迷后，悄悄取消了巡演日期</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="性感红。图片来源：凯特琳·莫里斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Kaitlyn-Morris_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于门票销量低迷<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sexyy-red">，性感红</a>取消了即将举行的巡演日期。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-talks-lancey-foux-motherhood-and-being-the-female-gucci-mane-3469882">Sexyy Red 谈论 Lancey Foux、母性以及成为“女性 Gucci Mane”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 7 月，这位说唱歌手宣布她将于今年晚些时候进行自己的“Sexyy Red 4 President”巡回演唱会。然而，很快就有传言称 Red 的第二次头条巡演并未按计划销售。根据<a href="https://x.com/ArtOfDialogue_/status/1810089591841468421?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1810401155194769919%7Ctwgr%5E1c9d4f15430283b25351ad746a916feee09eb1c6%7Ctwcon%5Es3_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fpost.php%3Fpost%3D3773291action%3Dedit" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Art Of Dialogue</em></a> and <a href="https://x.com/touringdata/status/1808576471771865597" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Touring Data的数据</em></a>，85,217张门票中仅售出37.11%。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-denies-reports-of-low-tickets-sales-we-not-cancelling-no-tour-3773291">不久之后，雷德对这些说法提出了异议</a>，并引用了该博客网站的推文来澄清事实：“我的粉丝正在买票，[而且]我们做得很好。我们不会取消任何旅行。取消所有大写字母[帽子表情符号]。”</p><p>但现在，巡演的一些演出已被取消，且没有任何解释。 <a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/sexyy-red-reshuffles-4-president-tour-dates-pushes-back-kick-off-1235758551/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>据Billboard</em></a>报道，巡演昨晚（8月22日）在西雅图的首次约会被取消，原计划在波特兰和奥克兰的约会也已悄然从行程中删除。</p><p> Red 尚未对取消日期做出任何解释，巡演将于周六（8 月 24 日）在亚特兰大 State Farm Arena 开始。</p><p>这一消息是在今年由于销量低迷而被迫取消巡演的趋势日益明显的情况下发生的。</p><p>今年夏天早些时候，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">黑键乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-the-black-keys-cancel-entire-2024-north-america-arena-tour-3759504">整个“国际球员巡演”被突然取消</a>，但没有提供任何解释。不久之后，人们猜测此举是因为门票销售量低而做出的， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-break-silence-explain-why-cancel-north-american-tour-3759601">成员们公开了取消的消息</a>，称该计划已被削减并重新规划，以支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-add-third-london-brixton-academy-show-to-spring-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-3609204">最近欧洲演出中较小的剧院场地</a>。</p><p>同样，本周早些时候，90 年代另类摇滚重量级人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/helmet">Helmet</a>宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/helmet-cancel-us-tour-following-financial-concerns-and-lower-than-expected-ticket-sales-3786047">由于财务问题和门票销售量低，他们取消了即将举行的美国巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauryn-hill">Lauryn Hill</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fugees">The Fugees</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lauryn-hill-and-the-fugees-have-quietly-cancelled-their-us-tour-3781582">最近也悄悄取消了他们的美国巡演</a>，Pras Michel 随后出面<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pras-discusses-cancelled-tour-with-lauryn-hill-and-the-fugees-my-frustration-was-for-the-fans-3785895">证实这一决定是由于门票销售不佳所致</a>。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/fugees-tour-canceled-pras-lauryn-hill.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a>采访时，普拉斯表示，乐队过去的巡演经历——即希尔因演出迟到几个小时而闻名——可能影响了销量不佳。</p><p>高昂的巡演成本也导致演出不得不取消巡演。本周早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">雷切尔·奇努里里 (Rachel Chinouriri)</a>宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rachel-chinouriri-cancels-us-dates-with-remi-wolf-due-to-financial-strain-of-touring-3785332">由于财务压力“太大”，</a>她已退出即将举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/remi-wolf">雷米·沃尔夫 (Remi Wolf)</a>巡演和多个音乐节时段。</p><p>硬核乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-armed">The Armed</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-armed-cancel-us-tour-the-finances-of-an-indie-band-across-the-board-are-quite-tenuous-3785748">最近也宣布，由于类似的财务压力，他们不得不取消今年预定的美国巡演</a>。</p><p>即使是老牌乐队也感受到了压力， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-chemical-brothers/">The Chemical Brothers</a>透露他们跳过了美国，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-say-touring-in-the-us-is-not-really-viable-at-the-moment-3498787">“成本上涨了很多”。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3785375" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785375" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785375" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg" alt="性感红。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sexyy-Red.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785375" class="wp-caption-text">性感红。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-reds-lip-loss-line-shades-include-gonorrhea-coochie-juice-and-blue-ballz-3785372">Red 本周早些时候宣布了一个新的唇彩系列，并以非常规的名字让粉丝们感到惊讶</a>。这是她即将推出的美容品牌 Northside Princess 中的第一款产品，这款唇彩不适合胆小的人，名为“Cochie Juice”、“Bootyhole Brown”、“Nut”、“Pussyhole Pink”、“Yellow Discharge”、“Gonorria” 、“Blue Ballz”和“在我的经期做爱”。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-believe